item.title: Aspose.ZIP for Java 23.12 Release Notes
item.description: This page contains release notes information for Aspose.ZIP for Java 23.12. This is the first public release of Aspose.ZIP for Java. Aspose.ZIP for Java currently supports Zip format and Store, Deflate, Deflate64 compression methods. Other file formats and compression methods will be supported soon.
